node.text: Love 🤩
Haha well done! Gorgeous pics

Stages of Reopening announced and not much is changing so I’m conjuring a little happy with a makeshift shoot in my bedroom…again. #Day117 .
.
.
So many little secrets in this photo. The background? An @innikachoo dress hanging on my closet door and taped up to cover the expanse (it’s a big dress). The top? Oh it’s my pajamas. What’s on the bottom? My @erikapenaofficial dress rolled into a makeshift skirt (this is often done on beauty shoots). The headscarf: Well, I tried to tie a turban to cover my dirty hair and it just wouldn’t tie right so I gave up and did a pirate look. Don’t believe me? Swipe 👈🏻. But the jewels are straight up gorgeous and no tricks or styling hacks were needed for these beauties! .
.
.
Earrings and Ring (current): @esmecrystals available at @houseofrajput 
Top (past season): @asos 
Scarf: @hermes (how’s that for high street meet high end??)
Lip: EMPOWERED by @natashamoorcosmetics by @natasha.moor
@ticbyrd that’s accidental. But thank you!
Gorgeous! Love how the scarf matches your eyes. 💕
@doux_singapore when you run out of ideas and spaces to shoot just delve into the depths of your wardrobe. Did it again today!
Gorgeous 😍! What a fabulous idea to use a dress as a background 👏👏👏
@konacoco_style thank you! Her stuff is fabulous!
Such a clever clogs! Amazing jewellery 😍
@fwstyle thank you. Just very bored.
Gorgeous! So creative 😍
@falak_amaar thank you! 🤗
Love it!
@elyseandi_official so effing depressing. Drink your way out.
It'sa bit depressing isn't it.  You look amazing though x
@kelkelster thank you! Doing my best!
Amazing such a pro

Such a beautiful and creative shoot! 😍
Love your make up🤗

Gorgeous!  Love the grey/blue tones in this picture.
@chetna_bhatt I have nothing to do but count. 😅
@sabrinasikora 😂
Is it Day 117... I stopped counting! Loving the ‘behind the scenes’ too🤩
@florencesorgini thank you! Do you do pale pink tops yet?
Looking beautiful!
@gayatriisingh you are very kind. So is photoshop. 😂
Dead drop gorgeous 😍
@instantgoddess thank you! Did something similar again today. Thank the lord for big dresses
Makeshift or not, still gorgeous and utterly fabulous! Nicely done! 👌✨

👏🏼👏🏼👏🏼 so stunning

So clever!! You exude confidence and beauty!
Love 🤩
Haha well done! Gorgeous pics
